{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: T-1000's shiny cop shoe.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The mercury blob crawls and rejoins the main mass, disappearing into the "shoe".
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 81 INT./EXT. SECURITY CAR
