{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Blythe runs to Dyson and hugs him, wailing.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BLYTHE
{DIALOGUE}: Don't hurt my father!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{META_DATA}: (screaming)
{DIALOGUE}: Shut up, kid!
{DIALOGUE}: Get out of the way!!
