{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Dyson looks at her, Terminator, then John.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sees his answer.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: DYSON
{DIALOGUE}: Now?
{META_DATA}: (he takes a breath)
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah, right.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He turns to his wife.
