{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Tarissa puts her hands on his arm.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She is stunned by what she's heard, but dealing with it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She believe them.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TARISSA
{DIALOGUE}: Miles, I'm scared.
