{DIALOGUE}: Go to a hotel.
{DIALOGUE}: Right now.
{DIALOGUE}: Don't pack.
{META_DATA}: (to the others)
{DIALOGUE}: Let's go.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{META_DATA}: 138B EXT, HIGHWAY - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Pavement rushing at us, lit by headlights.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Beyond, darkness.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH (V.O.)
