{DIALOGUE}: We were in uncharted territory now... making up history as we went along.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: TILT UP to reveal a rectangle of light ahead.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Cyberdyne Building...
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 139 INT. CYBERDYNE SYSTEMS BUILDING/LOBBY - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: TIGHT ON A CARD-KEY SCANNER as Dyson's hand zips his security card through a slot in one motion.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: There is the sound of a servo-lock, and --
{META_DATA}: 139A DYSON enter the spacious lobby, followed by Sarah, John, and
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator last of all.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: In a frontal angle, the others block Terminator from view.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: THE GUARD at the front desk, GIBBONS, looks up as Dyson moves toward him.
