{CHARACTER_NAME}: SARAH
{DIALOGUE}: Don't even think about it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Gibbons nods.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He stays frozen.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator circles quickly and gets the guard out of the chair.
