{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Before the thunderclap has faded Terminator walks into the fire and smoke.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: John goes back to work without missing a beat.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah and a stunned Dyson walk through the burning doorframe into the Artificial Intelligence Lab.
