{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 150 INT. LAB
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah and Terminator are working like a crack team, rigging the explosives.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She is taping the claymores to the gas cans with duct tape to create powerful incendiary bombs.
