{CHARACTER_NAME}: TERMINATOR
{DIALOGUE}: Radio remote.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He makes a plunger-pushing motion with his thumb and an accompanying "click" sound.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Dyson nods.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Just then John comes running in, holding up the key.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JOHN
{DIALOGUE}: I got it.
