{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It draws a Hoechler and Koch MPK machine pistol and cruises slowly into the firelit offices, scanning.
{META_DATA}: 172A IN THE CORRIDOR the bike skirts flaming wreckage as it idles forward.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: T-1000 scans the leaping shadows for its prey.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 173 INT. GROUND FLOOR/ELEVATOR/LOBBY
