{META_DATA}: 173E THEIR POV -- on the wall of boiling smoke. A FIGURE APPEARS. Walking
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Totally unaffected.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator emerges from the smoke.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Not even misty-eyed.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Not what they expected.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LEADER
{META_DATA}: (through megaphone)
{DIALOGUE}: Stop where you are.
{DIALOGUE}: Lie down on the floor, face down.
{DIALOGUE}: Down on floor, now!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He continues to stride toward them.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The SWATs tense up.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They've never seen anything like this.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They're not sure what to do.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Closer and closer.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LEADER
{DIALOGUE}: Drop him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They OPEN FIRE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The corridor is filled with CRACKING THUNDER.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The rounds tear into Terminator's chest.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Stomach.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Face.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Thighs.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His leather jacket leaps and jerks as the rounds hit him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The SWATs think the guy's wearing body armor or something.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They keep firing.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The rounds tear into him, staggering him slightly, but he keeps moving.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LEADER
{DIALOGUE}: You're not hitting him!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SWAT #1
{META_DATA}: (getting scared)
{DIALOGUE}: Yes I am!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator draws his .45 smoothly.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Unhurried.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He shoots the nearest man in the left thigh.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As he screams and drops, Terminator shoots him in the right thigh.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator bends down and picks up the shrieking man's weapon... the TEAR-GAS LAUNCHER.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It is one of those new rotary jobs that hold 12 rounds in a big drum.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator shoots the next SWAT in the chest with the tear-gas launcher.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The gas canister hits the guy's body armor and doesn't penetrate.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: But it's like getting slugged in the stomach with a full- swing from a baseball bat.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The SWAT fold double and hits the tiles, gasping.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator is an image from Hell, a tall figure in shredded black leather, streaked with blood.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: One eye is a bloody socket, the metal eye-servo glistening.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The flesh of one cheek hangs down in tatters, revealing the chrome cheekbone beneath.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The whole front of his jacket is blown open, revealing his metal armor chest.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The remaining SWATs start to fall back.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: One turns to run and -- KPOW!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A gas canister nail him in the back, sending him sprawling.
{META_DATA}: 173F Terminator fires three gas canisters into the lobby. It fills
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: rapidly with the white gas, cutting the visibility to a few feet.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It is total pandemonium.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SWAT LEADER crouches in the fog, white- knuckling the rifle.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator looms suddenly out of the mist right in front of him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: POOM!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator drills him in the leg with the .45.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As the guy screams and drops rifle to clutch his leg, Terminator rips his gas mask off.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The SWAT leader drops writhing to the floor, choking and gagging, clutching his bleeding thigh.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator walks up to two SWATs at the front doors.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: POW-POW.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leg and leg.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He snatches their masks as they fall.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The gunfire has stopped.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Nobody an see anything.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Screams and whimpers echo in the smoke.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 174 EXT. BUILDING
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Smoke boils out of the front door as a figure emerges.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Firing the tear-gas launcher with one hand, Terminator launches all remaining rounds among the cop vehicles.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Unprotected officers run, choking and half-blind, slamming into cars and tripping over each other.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It is a total rout.
{META_DATA}: 175 AT THE SWAT VAN on of the SWATs is rapidly handing out the remaining
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: masks to unprotected cops.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A FIGURE appears out of the smoke beside him.
