{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Then she grabs two M-16s from the wall-rack and loads them.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She starts on a shotgun as --
{META_DATA}: 180 The SWAT van weaves through sparse traffic at high speed.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Terminator slews the unstable van around cars and trucks which seem to be crawling.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The van hits it top speed of eighty.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They swerve to miss the back end of A WHITE 18-WHEEL TANKER.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 180A The chopper swings in behind them, closing fast.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 180B T-1000 reaches through the shattered canopy with the MPK machine pistol and FIRES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The back of the can CLANGS WITH HITS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The door windows are BLOWN IN.
