{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The unstable vehicle screeches and wobbles on the edge of control.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: One of the doors is kicked open.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sarah, wearing a ballistic vest, crouches in the doorway, whipping up the M-16.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SHE OPENS FIRE.
{META_DATA}: 180C Bullets riddle what's left of the chopper's canopy as the T-1000
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: returns fire.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The van is stitched with hits.
{META_DATA}: 180D INSIDE THE VAN holes are punched through the thin sheet-metal walls,
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ripping up the interior.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The vests covering John are hit repeatedly.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: We see that Sarah has hung two Kevlar vests on the inside of the back door and she ducks behind these as bullets hit around her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She pops back out and fires in controlled bursts.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The M-16 empties and she grabs another.
{META_DATA}: 180E Terminator serves around a car which is changing lanes, hitting it
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: and knocking it skidding.
{META_DATA}: 181 OMITTED
